The paper deals with techniques to extract watermark features from images and improve image search quality, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of deep convolutional neural networks (CNNs) also suggests a focus on multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the analysis of images based on their domains, which could potentially fall under computer security (cs.CR).
